@startuml
!include ../../styles/plantuml-theme.puml

title FIG-04-06. Payment Instruction Lifecycle State Machine

state "Screening Pending" as ScreeningPending
state "Posting Pending" as PostingPending
state "Sent to Scheme" as SentToScheme

[*] --> Received : submitted / create
Received --> Validated : checksPassed
Validated --> ScreeningPending : requestScreening

ScreeningPending --> Rejected : screeningResult [failed]\n/ recordRejection
ScreeningPending --> PostingPending : screeningResult [passed]\n/ requestPosting

PostingPending --> Accepted : postingResult [accepted]\n/ recordAccepted
PostingPending --> Failed : postingResult [failed]\n/ recordFailure

Accepted --> SentToScheme : sent
SentToScheme --> Settled : settled

Rejected --> [*]
Settled --> [*]
Failed --> [*]

note bottom
  Transition labels use event [guard] / effect.
  Repair, cancellation and resubmission are excluded.
end note
@enduml
